tossup_question: -   –  What is the resistance, in ohms, of a resistor that has a 20 milliampere current when connected across the terminals of a 1.5 volt battery?
bonus_question: -   –  A 2 kilogram box is sliding across a frictionless surface at 4 meters per second to the north. A 6 newton force directed to the south acts on the box for 2 seconds. What is the final speed, in meters per second, and direction of the box?
